data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS This single-family residence is situated just 2 blocks from the beach and offers an incredible opportunity for those looking to personalize and renovate a home to their taste and style.  AN ENTERTAINER'S DREAM! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom open concept bungalow boasts a cathedral ceiling and gas burning fireplace in the living area. A breakfast area with sliding glass doors that lead to an 11' x 10' concrete patio which lends direct access to a 24' x 17' L-shaped deck with built in benches.  On the back of the home is a 15' x 12' sunroom to be enjoyed for an evening of entertaining or an afternoon nap.  Location is key and being just a short walk to the beautiful white sand beaches in an area with many restaurants, shopping and entertainment, this property offers not just a home but a lifestyle.  New roof in 2022.  Square Footage Agent measured.  If important, please confirm for accuracy.
